Elegant Living Decorating is an interior decor company that
offers a variety of residential decor services to beautify your 
home. Good taste, loads of ideas and creative vision, will  ensure
happiness in your space. What are you waiting for?  
Services include: Color Consultation, space planning, flooring,
room make-overs, draperies, bedding, art/accessory advice and seasonal/holiday. Decor Solutions for your home.
Visit website elegantlivingdecorating.ca
